1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Totalmente Demais (English: Totally Awesome) is a Brazilian telenovela based on the play Pygmalion by George Bernard Shaw in 1913. It stars Marina Ruy Barbosa, Juliana Paes, Felipe Simas and Fabio Assunção as the main protagonists. Paulo Rocha and Priscila Steinmain as the central antagonists.
